descript.purpose: To present a polygon geography for use in GIS applications that was somewhere between census tracts (too small) and wards (too big). Neighbourhoods are approximate representations of historical-economic areas, with strong emphasis on income variables.

theme.themekt: REQUIRED: Reference to a formally registered thesaurus or a similar authoritative source of theme keywords.

idinfo.accconst: None for base polygons. Census data should attached and used only through the guidelines of the PCT Research Sub-Committee.
